<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="14Mar1924"><font color="red">14 March 1924</font> LUND (to Richard Wallace): May I trouble you to return this book to Mrs Wallace and thank her. I am afraid I am a day or two overdue but I have been working very hard. I have finished the Shem-Cain piece and also the Anna Livia one. If you ever wish to hear them let me know. The dentist, I hope, will finish with my wife tomorrow. </div>
